{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-markdown-js","path":"/components/ez-link","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Links allow users to navigate to other pages in an application. Links can be presented as standalone text or inline inside a paragraph, or used to enhance other elements, like headings or images, with navigation behavior.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"best-practices\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#best-practices\" aria-label=\"best practices permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Best Practices</h2>\n<p>Link should:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Clearly indicate the destination of the navigation using text or images with assistive text.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Links should not:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Be used for embedding actions or submitting data. Consider <a href=\"/recipe/components/ez-button\">buttons</a> for this usage.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<h3 id=\"text-link\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#text-link\" aria-label=\"text link permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Text link</h3>\n<p>Used for either stand-alone navigational actions or links within larger spans of text.</p>\n<p>Links accept any <a href=\"https://flow.org/en/docs/react/types/#toc-react-element\">ReactElement</a> as children. The link component will add Recipe's styles and event handlers to that element. Actual navigation will be handled by the wrapped element.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">&#x3C;EzLink>\n  &#x3C;a href=\"/orders\">View Orders&#x3C;/a>\n&#x3C;/EzLink>\n</code></pre>\n<p>To use with React Router</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-tsx\">import {EzLink} from '@ezcater/recipe';\nimport {Link as RouterLink} from 'react-router-dom';\n\n&#x3C;EzLink>\n  &#x3C;RouterLink to=\"/next-page\">Next Page&#x3C;/RouterLink>\n&#x3C;/EzLink>;\n</code></pre>\n<p>If the ReactNode provided to the link component is plain text, it will be styled and exposed to assistive technologies as a link. Interaction will need to be handled in JavaScript with the <code>onClick</code> prop. Note: this will not behave like a native link. Browser features like context menus and open in new tab will not be available.</p>\n<h3 id=\"secondary-links\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#secondary-links\" aria-label=\"secondary links permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Secondary links</h3>\n<p>The <code>secondary</code> link variant matches the current color of the containing paragraph text. Its subdued appearance is suitable when the primary variant is too overwhelming, such as in blocks of text with several references linked throughout.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">&#x3C;p>\n  These earnings roll into your total &#x3C;EzLink use=\"secondary\">ezRewards&#x3C;/EzLink>. Use as payment on\n  any order at checkout.\n&#x3C;/p>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"reset-links\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reset-links\" aria-label=\"reset links permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reset links</h3>\n<p>The <code>reset</code> link variant removes the browser default text decoration and color from the wrapped navigation element. This variant can be used to provide navigation semantics to other elements, such as headings or charts, without impacting their default appearance.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">&#x3C;EzLink use=\"reset\">\n  &#x3C;a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\">\n    &#x3C;Placeholder>This placeholder is a link&#x3C;/Placeholder>\n  &#x3C;/a>\n&#x3C;/EzLink>\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"related-components\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#related-components\" aria-label=\"related components permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related components</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/recipe/components/ez-button\">Button</a></li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Links allow users to navigate to other pages in an application. Links can be presented as standalone text or inline inside a paragraph, or used to enhance other elements, like headings or images, with navigation behavior."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"best-practices","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#best-practices","ariaLabel":"best practices permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2